n<br />\n何況係支那 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你咪理樓上班on9啦<br />\n連無人會去支那旅行都講得出 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36d5b3202d000f1447e42631ec06efdde85b062c","tid":281083,"uid":58081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T16:33:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你咪當交學費囉<br />\n咁你都信<br />\n咁大條水魚梗係呃啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n內地啲嘢你唔好諗住追得返<br />\n呢啲咁嘅黑店多數有備而來<br />\n你諗住帶多幾個朋友一齊上去<br />\n到時畀人困住咗要畀錢贖人仲煩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都唔好覺得報公安有用<br />\n內地畀錢疏通下就無事<br />\n呃你萬幾蚊<br />\n佢拎一半出嚟同公安對分就乜事都無<br />\n話唔埋畀多少少錢搵人趁你係內地就搞返你轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n內你老母咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f4e758f52c2a3a109fca1e6a2a9930d0dd0b2dc","tid":281083,"uid":8717,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T16:35:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/13/003502_1146ea370241138a3f1eccc72121d598.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F13%2F003502_1146ea370241138a3f1eccc72121d598.jpg&h=4d0c542c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n樓主買左幾錢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a59dda61888fe8b5754b84a72d8de41ce136a0a","tid":281083,"uid":414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T16:35:54.000Z","msg":"邊間旅行社<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f225ae3d80aef1aee651a5ddfb5f20b050bf0db","tid":281083,"uid":54371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T16:40:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主你可以聯絡旅行社，話個時領隊又好，導遊又好，點解明知呢d係呃人手段，都可以咁樣比佢地水自己團友<br />\n<br />\n我都唔知佢地講左咩令到最後有得refund</blockquote><br />\n正常都有得refund<br />\n