al/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跟住就係當好多人去冰島都自由行嗰陣，樓豬去大陸都要跟團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />然後就係到咗2017年嘅今日，竟然仲會有人中呢啲垃圾購物點嘅伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你幾十歲都仲話可能無受過教育，無知俾人呃啦。大佬你後生仔呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你話睇阿樓豬個款可能都無受過教育呢？咁你都有睇下新聞掛！都有接觸下個社會發生緊乜事掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4771cd71504b02047da5192366cdde89fb144c8","tid":281083,"uid":24519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T21:22:33.000Z","msg":"三位數字我笑撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當上一課啦，咁撚蠢"},{"pid":"8b0bd8e695d3c7cbb60bbba39ab83a83ef290d9e","tid":281083,"uid":45498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T21:35:53.000Z","msg":"支那遊 抵你死啦 有日本唔去？我寫埋旅遊攻略俾你又點話<br />\n<br />\nPlan唔切夾硬去，唔熟地方當地無親戚朋友仲去？<br />\n<br />\n你去狗寨溝 唔係為咗睇風景咩？睇玉做咩撚野？<br />\n<br />\n即場減價十倍 你都知有問題啦樓豬<br />\n<br />\n塊膠玉 有咩值得你去買？食得㗎？一舊裝飾品五位數買，證明你其實貪小便宜，以為執到寶<br />\n「便宜莫貪！」 <br />\n<br />\n你老母真係俾你激死<br />\n睇下新聞了解下個世界發生咩事啦<br />\n<br />\n都十幾廿歲人啦，無獨立思考能力，真係可悲"},{"pid":"a08e020a0a0cb180740718d917e8ca0e590e0c13","tid":281083,"uid":78732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T21:59:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/503282/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E5%9C%98%E9%80%9B%E9%BB%91%E5%BA%97%E7%8F%BE%E5%BD%B1%E5%B8%9D%E7%B4%9A%E9%A8%99%E5%AD%90\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F503282%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E